ğŸ¯ Project Goal

Develop a system capable of:
- Generating an interactive quiz based on questions stored in a structured document
- Converting this document into JSON
- Transforming the JSON into a dynamically generated Google Form, using the Google Forms API as a reference
- Providing a functional, scalable, and easily integrable API

